Description: GNOME thumbnailer for pictures in native formats of
 Amiga, Amstrad CPC, Apple II, Atari 8-bit/Portfolio/ST/TT/Falcon,
 BBC Micro, Commodore VIC-20/64/16/116/Plus4/128, Electronika BK, FM Towns,
 HP 48, Macintosh 128K, MSX, NEC PC-80/88/98, Oric, Psion Series 3, SAM Coupe,
 Sharp X68000, Tandy 1000, Timex 2048, TRS-80, TRS-80 Color Computer,
 Vector-06C, ZX81 and ZX Spectrum computers.

